summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of Two Hundred Seventy-five Dollars ($275.00) or as much thereof as may be necessary, as appropriated from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, by Ordinance No. 31172, for the purpose of extending First Avenue South, to the First Avenue South Condemnation Fund, under Ordinance No. 31581, for the purpose of paying the cost of said condemnation.
